id=blockgms_sysupdate
name=Block GMS System Update (Google TV)
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=cavecrew
description=Disables the Google Play Services system-update COMPONENTS (SystemUpdateService/GcmTaskService/PersistentListener + the Check-for-updates UI) so an A/B OTA cannot be fetched/applied and clobber an internal CoreELEC dual-boot. GMS core (Play, accounts, casting, app updates) is untouched. Reversible: remove this module + `pm enable` the components. Generic to Google/Android TV boxes.
